<asp:Content ID="Content3" ContentPlaceHolderID="bodyContent" Runat="Server">
    <div class="bs-docs-section">
        <div class="page-header">
            <h2>Getting Started</h1>
        </div>  
        <p class="lead">This is your place to buy what you want and make a few friends while you're at it. Here's how to get started:</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h4>1.  Register</h4>
                <p class="marginLeft20">You can browse for items as a guest, you can buy, and also register. As a member you can:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Buy on E-trade</li>
                    <li>Track up to 200 items at a time</li>
                    <li>Use E-trade account to manage your buying activities</li>
                    <li>When you're ready, register to get started</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h4>2.  Read information for new members</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>When you register you'll be asked to read and agree to our User Agreement.</li>
                    <li>Find answers to frequently asked questions in Contact Us. Stay in touch with our community.</li>
                    <li>We have a number of community resources to help you stay informed about the latest events, programs, and news.</li>
                    <li>Use E-trade account to help you track and manage your buying, account information, and preferences.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h4>3.  Learn about trust and safety on E-trade</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Beware of spoof (fake)emails that claim to be sent by E-trade.</li>
                    <li>They ask you to reply with personal information, such as your credit card number or account password.</li>
                    <li>Learn how to spot a spoof email and what to do about it.</li>
                    <li>To help create a safe and fair trading environment, we have rules and policies for all members.</li>
                    <li>To help keep you safe when buying, we also offer protection programs for buyers.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h4>4.  Start buying</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>When you're ready to start buying, begin by searching or browsing for items you're interested in.</li>
                    <li>There are lots of ways to buy. Learn about the different ways you can buy.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</asp:Content>

